#

Roasted Pork Loin with Garlic Smashed Potatoes

$25
680 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

PorkComfort FoodMain Course

Description

Succulent roasted pork loin paired with creamy garlic mashed potatoes, perfect for a hearty meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork Loin: 2 lbs
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Garlic: 6 cloves
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Rosemary: 1 tsp
